{
  "stem": "6719.6",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He brought me Hershey chocolates in a satchel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "After the first day I, couldn't look at a chocolate anymore, even if it killed me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I gave it to my boy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was the most popular, I was to be called a chocolate boy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Schokolad-- the schokoladenjunge, that was me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Couldn't eat it any more.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Now, I wanted something else.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he kept on telling me, and telling me, and telling me, and gave me a picture.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[SIGHS] I still got it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Changed my name, which I didn't keep.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He says, Adolf, that shit name, he said.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He had Johnny.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I didn't like Johnny.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Later on, I changed it to Dennis.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Did you ever know his last name?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, just Paul.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have a picture, and it says on there, good luck, uh-- good luck, Jo-- good luck, Johnny.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Paul.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's all I know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was the-- that was the boy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Greatest thing in the world.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's funny.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's, uh-- [SIGHS] you know, uh, I--I--I-- I'm-- I'm-- I'm saying this almost at the very end.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The, uh-- I learned a lesson-- but it's a different lesson than some people say, I learned a lesson from this-- that, if something happens to you, after you go through all this, no matter what, even if you think it's bad, I mean real bad-- bad, bad, bad-- sit down for 10 seconds and say, that's bad?",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And think back what happened in 19 hundred 43, or 44, or 45, every day, every minute of the time you spent there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then you say, what the hell am I squawking about?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "How can it be bad today?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's nothing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't want always stick to that-- to that resolution, but at least I try to make myself stick to it, so.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My pleasure.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
